OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FAward-winning rapper Ghetts has been
OL,7,Fjailed for 12 years for killing a
OL,8,Fstudent in a hit and run while
OL,9,Fspeeding and over the drink-drive
OL,10,Flimit.The grime artist, whose real
OL,11,Fname is Justin Clarke-Samuel, failed
OL,12,Fto stop after his BMW hit Nepalese
OL,13,Fnational Yubin Tamang, 20, in north-
OL,14,Feast London.
OL,16,FThe 41-year-old defendant admitted
OL,17,Fcausing death by dangerous driving and
OL,18,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FIn a televised sentencing at the Old
OL,7,FBailey, Judge Mark Lucraft KC handed
OL,8,Fhim 12 years in prison and
OL,9,Fdisqualified him from driving for 17
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FHe told Clarke-Samuel that CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage showed a "quite appalling
OL,14,Flitany of incidents" leading up to the
OL,15,Ffatal collision which was "simply
OL,16,Fshocking".
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@TO]wD@[OUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FThe judge noted the father-of-two's
OL,7,F"genuine remorse" and letters of
OL,8,Fsupport including from his partner
OL,9,Fsetting out how he had used his career
OL,10,Fin music to make a positive impact on
OL,11,Fhis community.
OL,13,FProsecutor Philip McGhee said Clarke-
OL,14,FSamuel had been drinking alcohol at
OL,15,FOmi Lounge in Wells Street in central
OL,16,FLondon on the evening of Saturday
OL,17,FOctober 18 2025.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FHe was said to be one-and-a-half times
OL,7,Fover the legal drink-drive limit and
OL,8,Fwas driving at speeds of more than
OL,9,F70mph before the crash.
OL,11,FAs he drove his BMW M5 at speed back
OL,12,Ftowards his home in Woodford, east
OL,13,FLondon, he failed to stop at six red
OL,14,Ftraffic lights, the court was told.
OL,16,FHe repeatedly veered on to the wrong
OL,17,Fside of the road, mounted the curb and
OL,18,Fcollided with a motorcyclist and a
OL,19,FMercedes, causing damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FHe was going 67mph in a 30mph zone
OL,7,Fbefore he hit Mr Tamang as he crossed
OL,8,FRedbridge Lane, Ilford, at 11.33pm.
OL,10,FMr McGhee said: "Mr Tamang was still
OL,11,Fcrossing the road. He could do nothing
OL,12,Fto avoid a collision. The defendant's
OL,13,FBMW ploughed into him. Mr Tamang was
OL,14,Fcatapulted into the air before
OL,15,Fcrashing down on the roadway. He
OL,16,Fsustained catastrophic injuries."
OL,18,FThe defendant failed to stop and drove
OL,19,Feight miles home, arriving over 15
OL,20,Fminutes later.
OL,26,@rD@QOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FThe defendant made no call to
OL,7,Femergency services and Mr Tamang died
OL,8,Fin hospital from his injuries two days
OL,9,Flater.
OL,11,FThe court was shown a compilation of
OL,12,FCCTV of Clarke-Samuel's erratic
OL,13,Fdriving including graphic footage of
OL,14,Fthe moment he hit Mr Tamang.
OL,16,FPolice went to Clarke-Samuel's home in
OL,17,FWoodford in the early hours of the
OL,18,Fnext day and smelled alcohol on his
OL,19,Fbreath before arresting him.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FOfficers found his black BMW was
OL,7,Fsignificantly damaged with a smashed
OL,8,Fwindscreen and damage to the front
OL,9,Fbumper.
OL,11,FThe court was told the defendant had
OL,12,Fclaimed he had driven dangerously
OL,13,Fbecause he feared someone was
OL,14,Ffollowing him but no evidence of a
OL,15,Fpursuit was found on CCTV.
OL,17,FThe defendant had 12 previous
OL,18,Fconvictions for 27 crimes from the age
OL,19,Fof 16 including robbery, aggravated
OL,20,Fvehicle taking and driving offences.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FWeeping in court, Mr Tamang's mother
OL,7,FSharmila Tamang said: "My son had come
OL,8,Ffor studies to this place but because
OL,9,Fof somebody's mistakes he has died at
OL,10,Fa very small age. Yubin was our only
OL,11,Fchild.
OL,13,F"My son had come for his studies to
OL,14,Fthe UK saying the UK had the best
OL,15,Fdegree in the world. But on his way
OL,16,Fback from his work this happened and
OL,17,Fhe lost his life."
OL,26,@oD@WOUuD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FMr Tamang's roommate Sushant Khadka
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement read to the court:
OL,8,F"Yubin was only 20 years old. He had
OL,9,Fdreams, ambition, plans for his
OL,10,Ffuture."
OL,12,FHe said the incident had not only led
OL,13,Fto the loss of a life "full of
OL,14,Fpromise", it had also permanently
OL,15,Faffected the lives of others.
OL,17,FIn mitigation, Ben Aina KC read out
OL,18,Fextracts of a letter Clarke-Samuel had
OL,19,Fwritten apologising to Mr Tamang's
OL,20,Ffamily.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@HO]uD@WOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FThe rapper stated: "I write from a
OL,7,Fplace of extreme regret, shame and
OL,8,Fremorse. I am fully aware that there
OL,9,Fare no number of apologies that I can
OL,10,Fsay which will soothe the pain that
OL,11,Fthe family and friends of Mr Tamang
OL,12,Fmust feel.
OL,14,F"This may be the only chance that I
OL,15,Fget to apologise. It was truly an
OL,16,Funintentional act on my part and I am
OL,17,Fso sincerely sorry for the suffering
OL,18,Fand emotional distress that I have
OL,19,Fcaused.
OL,26,@nD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,F"I fully understand that I must face
OL,7,Fconsequences for my actions and I
OL,8,Faccept that I must now be punished. I
OL,9,Fhope through the process of punishment
OL,10,Fand rehabilitation I can still add
OL,11,Fsome contribution to my community"
OL,13,FExplaining the root of the defendant's
OL,14,Ffears, Mr Aina said that in 2017,
OL,15,FClarke-Samuel had been robbed at
OL,16,Fgunpoint at a studio and although it
OL,17,Fhad been reported to police, the
OL,18,Fassailants were never caught.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FThe rapper was provided with a driver
OL,7,Fwhile working and usually took taxis
OL,8,Fwhen going out, Mr Aina added, saying:
OL,9,F"Sadly that was not the case on
OL,10,FOctober 18."
OL,12,FGhetts is a rapper and songwriter who
OL,13,Fhas collaborated on tracks with
OL,14,FSkepta, Stormzy and Ed Sheeran, and
OL,15,Fperformed at Glastonbury several times
OL,16,Fincluding in 2024.
OL,18,FHe won best male act at the 2021 Mobo
OL,19,FAwards and received the Mobo pioneer
OL,20,Faward in 2024.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FShani Taggart, of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, said: "Justin
OL,8,FClarke-Samuel knew he was in no fit
OL,9,Fstate to drive and there was clear
OL,10,Fevidence of his excessive speed and
OL,11,Fdisregard for road users as he drove
OL,12,Fincredibly dangerously across our city.
OL,14,F"After presenting this evidence, we
OL,15,Fsecured guilty pleas to these two
OL,16,Fcharges and today's sentence will see
OL,17,FClarke-Samuel face the consequences of
OL,18,Fhis fatal decision to get behind the
OL,19,Fwheel of a car after drinking."
OL,26,@oD@\OUvD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772550673
OL,3,CRap star Ghetts jailed for fatal hit-
OL,4,Cand-run which killed university student
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Faye Cook, who led
OL,7,Fthe Met's investigation, said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with Yubin's loved
OL,9,Fones, especially his parents, Sharmila
OL,10,Fand Bikash, who have shown remarkable
OL,11,Fcourage throughout this investigation.
OL,13,F"Their strength has inspired everyone
OL,14,Finvolved in the case.
OL,16,F"We hope today's sentencing brings
OL,17,Fsome measure of comfort to Yubin's
OL,18,Ffamily, while also serving as a
OL,19,Freminder to the public of the
OL,20,Fdevastating consequences of dangerous
OL,21,Fdriving."
OL,26,@oD@`OUxD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/14
